    "title": "Lead Revenue Manager at Six Senses India Capital India",
    "description": "If you're a passionate Revenue Manager with drive and ambition, Six Senses India Capital India in Rajkot is the place for you. We're growing fast and need talented people to grow with us.\n\nAbout Six Senses India Capital India:\nSix Senses India Capital India is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Ensure compliance with FSSAI, health, and safety regulations\n• Plan and execute banquets, events, and MICE functions\n• Prepare daily operating reports and present to management\n• Train and supervise front-line staff on service standards\n• Conduct regular guest satisfaction surveys and implement improvements\n• Manage procurement of hotel supplies and control operating costs\n• Handle guest complaints and resolve issues promptly\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• BPharm / MPharm / PharmD\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in OTA Management\n• Proficiency in GDS Systems\n• Proficiency in Hotel Management\n• Proficiency in Customer Relations\n• Proficiency in Travel Management\n• Proficiency in Yield Management\n• Proficiency in HACCP\n• Proficiency in Front Office\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Referral bonus program\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Flexible working hours\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Rajkot, Gujarat, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Six Senses India Capital India!",
